---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Software Validation">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-shield"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>End-to-end Software Validation &amp; QA</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies provides software validation with a strict process of test plan writing, execution, defect identification and recommendations, all the way to final release. Our services cover both white box and black box testing at any stage of the development lifecycle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-tasks"></i></div>
            <h5>White &amp; Black Box Testing</h5>
            <p>Flexible white box and black box testing by qualified testers, applicable at any stage of the software development process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-file-text"></i></div>
            <h5>Functional Testing</h5>
            <p>Functional and non-functional testing coverage, including thorough review of all project documentation at each milestone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-server"></i></div>
            <h5>Multi-platform Coverage</h5>
            <p>Testing across Windows, Linux, Solaris, AIX and HP-UX operating systems with support for all major web application servers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-database"></i></div>
            <h5>Database Testing</h5>
            <p>Validation across Oracle, SQL Server, IBM DB2, Sybase, MySQL and more — ensuring data integrity throughout your application.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-user-secret"></i></div>
            <h5>Third-party Validation</h5>
            <p>Objective, independent validation by a qualified third party — removing internal bias and providing credible sign-off on quality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-check"></i></div>
            <h5>On-time, High Quality</h5>
            <p>Complete testing coverage with affordable testing costs, guaranteeing on-time release without compromising on quality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
